%p
  You can update your email (with which teams will contact you) here. If you need to change your region/team affiliation, contact
  %a{href: "mailto: brownman@umich.edu"}<
    David Brownman
  with all necessary information.

.form_box
  %form{name: "settings", action: "settings", method: "post"}
    %label{for: "email"}
      Email
    %input{type: "email", name: "username", placeholder:"email", id: "email"}

    %label{for: "lang"}
      Language
    %select{name: "lang", id: "lang"}
      / these langauges are hardcoded, so update when you add a new lang
      %option{value: "EN"}
        English
      %option{value: "FR"}
        FranÃ§ais

    %input.button{type: "submit", value: "Update User"}

%p
  Below you can upload a profile picture. Aim for something mostly square and larger than 300px wide. You can use 
  %a{href: "http://www.picresize.com", target: "_blank"}<
    this
  site to easily crop and edit your photo. This will replace your current picture (which you can see on your
  %a{href: "/profile"}<
    profile
  page). 

.form_box
  %form{method: "post", enctype: "multipart/form-data", action: "upload"}
    %label{for: "myfile"}
      Image (max file size 5MB)
    %input{type: "file", name: "myfile"}   
    %br
    %input{type:'submit', value:'Upload!'}


%p
  %a{href: '/reset'}<
    Reset
  your password.

